pageContext.claim: “Now, he issued it on Friday night. We've all heard about that, Jon -- Friday nights, right? In fact, [Biden's] was later Friday night than I ever released mine on Friday night. Okay? So he did — he did it pretty late. I mean, you know, like at 11 o'clock in the evening or something.”
pageContext.analysis: The Fact Checker found no record of a late night Biden apology. Moreover, the Trump administration often releases news late on Friday nights.
